/bin/
/dist/
# Local database, snapshots, and any user-generated content. The
# directory itself is recreated at boot via os.MkdirAll, so we ignore
# the whole tree without keeping a .gitkeep around.
/data/
*.test
*.out
coverage.html
coverage.out
.DS_Store
.env
configs/*.local.yaml
.claude/
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
.tmp/
node_modules/

# Internal planning notes — kept on disk locally but never published.
PLAN.md
PLAN-*.md

# Local-only artefacts from MCP / browser tooling sessions —
# Playwright snapshots and screenshots Claude takes while working.
# README screenshots under docs/screenshots/ ARE tracked.
.playwright-mcp/
*.png
*.jpeg
*.jpg
!docs/screenshots/*.png
!docs/screenshots/*.jpeg
!docs/screenshots/*.jpg
!assets/*.png
!assets/*.jpeg
!assets/*.jpg
!web/static/*.png
!web/static/*.jpeg
!web/static/*.jpg

# Reference screenshots from third-party apps (raindrop.io etc.)
# kept locally as visual references for UX work — never published.
/screenshots/
